		<p class="lbl lbl-light">19 · Navy-700 / 1:1 / 2-col points grid / Image</p>
		<div class="wrapper wrapper--wide grid-half">
			<div class="text-col">
				<p class="tag tag--brand">Buying & Selling Property</p>
				<h2 class="heading heading--brand">Buying or selling property in Kilkenny?</h2>
				<p class="body body--brand">We manage the full conveyancing process from first instruction to completion.</p>
				<div class="points-grid">
					<div class="pg-item"><span class="pg-head">Contracts</span><span class="pg-body">Reviewed in full before you sign anything</span></div>
					<div class="pg-item"><span class="pg-head">Title</span><span class="pg-body">Checks, planning, and compliance handled</span></div>
					<div class="pg-item"><span class="pg-head">Mortgage</span><span class="pg-body">Lender requirements managed throughout</span></div>
					<div class="pg-item"><span class="pg-head">Completion</span><span class="pg-body">Coordinated from start to finish</span></div>
				</div>
